name: study
label: Study
description: Indicates whether table/measure is a core components of the study or belongs to a substudy / anxiliary study

name: domain
label: Domain
description: The broad domain that a table/measure belongs to

name: sub_domain
label: Subdomain
description: The smaller level category that a table/measure belongs to

name: source
label: Source
description: The source that provided data for this table/measure

name: metric
label: Metric
description: The specific imaging metric assessed in this table/measure
tooltip_info: Only used for tables in the "Imaging" domain

name: atlas
label: Atlas
description: The cortical or fiber tract atlas used for this table/measure
tooltip_info: Only used for tables in the "Imaging" domain

name: table_name
label: Table name
description: The name of the table/measure

name: table_label
label: Table label
description: The label of the table/measure

name: name
label: Variable name
description: The name of the column/variable/question

name: label
label: Variable label
description: The label of the column/variable/question
tooltip_info: Description in the NBDC Data Access Portal's data dictionary table

name: instruction
label: Instruction
description: The instructions <i>preceding all questions<i> in this table/measure
values_examples:
Example:
"The next set of question is about your childs behavior in different situations and contexts. Please fill in a response to all questions."

name: header
label: Header
description: The intermediate header/instructions pertaining to subset of questions that this column/variable/question belongs to
values_examples:
Example:
"We are now going to ask some questions about the birth and early development of the child who is participating in this study."

name: note
label: Note
description: The note displayed to participants for this column/variable/question

name: unit
label: Unit
description: The (scientific) unit that a column/variable is measured in

name: type_var
label: Variable type
description: The general type of the column/variable/question
tooltip_json: If type_var is one of "derived item" or "summary score", BIDS JSON element Derived is set to "true"; "false" otherwise

name: type_data
label: Data type
description: The data type of the column/variable/question (as represented in the data/database)

name: type_level
label: Level of measurement
description: The level of measurement (or scale type) of the column/variable/question

name: type_field
label: Field type
description: The field type of the column/variable/question in the electronic data capture system (i.e., how it was displayed to the participant)

name: order_display
label: Display order
description: The order (within a given measure) in which the column/variable/question was displayed to the participant

name: branching_logic
label: Branching logic
description: The branching logic that applied to the column/variable/question

name: label_es
label: Label (Spanish)
description: The Spanish label of the column/variable/question

name: instruction_es
label: Instruction (Spanish)
description: The Spanish instructions preceding all questions in this table/measure

name: header_es
label: Header (Spanish)
description: The Spanish intermediate header/instructions pertaining to subset of questions that this column/variable/question belongs to

name: note_es
label: Note (Spanish)
description: The Spanish note displayed to participants for this column/variable/question

name: table_nda
label: Table name (NDA)
description: The NDA table that this column/variable/question belonged to in the 4.0 and earlier releases

name: table_nda_5_0
label: Table name (NDA 5.0)
description: The NDA table that this column/variable/question belonged to in the 5.0/5.1 release

name: table_redcap
label: Table name (REDCap)
description: The REDCap table that this column/variable/question belongs to

name: name_nda
label: Variable name (NDA)
description: The name of this column/variable/question in NDA releases up to the 5.1 and earlier releases

name: name_deap
label: Variable name (DEAP 1.0)
description: The DEAP 1.0 name of this column/variable/question

name: name_redcap
label: Variable name (REDCap)
description: The name of this column/variable/question in REDCap

name: name_redcap_exp
label: Variable name (REDCap export)
description: The export name of this column/variable/question in REDCap

name: name_stata
label: Variable name (STATA)
description: The name of this column when downloaded from DEAP in STATA format

name: url_table
label: Table documentation
description: Hyperlink to the table's description in the data documentation

name: url_table_warn_use
label: Responsible data use warning (table)
description: Hyperlink to a warning about responsible data use for the table in the data documentation

name: url_table_warn_data
label: Data quality warning (table)
description: Hyperlink to a warning about data issues for the table in the data documentation

name: url_warn_use
label: Responsible data use warning (variable)
description: Hyperlink to a warning about responsible data use in the data documentation

name: url_warn_data
label: Data quality warning (variable)
description: Hyperlink to a warning about data issues in the data documentation

name: url_docs_ss
label: Summary score documentation
description: Hyperlink to a summary score's documentation in the ABCDscores R package

name: identifier_columns
label: Identifier column(s)
description: Unique identifier column name(s) for this variable/table

name: order_sort
label: Sort order
description: The standard sort order within a table/measure in the data dictionary table; also determines order of columns in data/database
